sequenceDiagram
    participant GP as Gameplay
    participant SS as SaveService
    participant IS as ISaveable collectors
    participant JU as JsonUtility
    participant FS as persistentDataPath/save.json

    GP->>SS: Save() on quit / autosave tick
    SS->>IS: GatherState()
    IS-->>SS: GameState struct (resources, upgrades, orbiters)
    SS->>JU: ToJson(state, prettyPrint: true)
    JU-->>SS: string
    SS->>FS: File.WriteAllText(path, json)
    FS-->>SS: done
